INSTALLATION

1. Copy the contents of the src folder (app and lib folder) to your Magento root directory
-- Clear cache if necessary

GLOBAL CONFIGURATION

1. Login into your Magento backend and goto System > Configuration > Catalog > Give It
2. Configure the module by filling in the public and private keys, button settings, and delivery options
3. Goto to the frontend and visit a simple product page, you will now see that the give it button is ready for action 

TURN ON/OFF BUTTON PER PRODUCT

1. Login into your Magento backend and goto Catalog > Manage Products
2. Choose to edit a simple product
3. Choose the general tab on the left menu
4. Configure the "Give It Button Active" setting 

